OL,7,FWhen Stephen Chance discovered his mum
OL,8,Fhad suddenly died as a result of a
OL,9,Fbrain aneurysm only hours after he had
OL,10,Flost his job, he felt numb and didn't
OL,11,Fknow what he was going to do.
OL,13,F"I thought 'what do I do' because my
OL,14,Fmum has just died and I'm grieving," he
OL,15,Frecalls. "I had recently broken up with
OL,16,Fthe boyfriend I had at the time as well
OL,17,Fso those three things were very
OL,18,Fdifficult."
OL,3,C'My mum died and I lost my job on the
OL,4,Csame day. Homelessness can strike out
OL,5,Cof the blue'
